data.description: "Can You Say WOW" this home confirms what is said about this neighborhood. You will find nothing but character and prestige through out. It must have been designed with entertaining in mind. It is set so almost all rooms have access to the glimmering pool which is situated in the center. Great for entertaining large or small groups of friends and family, or have some quiet time with your significant other. Inside this home it is so unique there can't be 2 like it. Owners have taken well care of this one. For more update information on this property please call 210-367-6024 or 210-454-8806 We have a list of foreclosures in this area and we can email them to you imme
